Okay?
We're going to Alaska?

31:57.583 --> 31:59.885
Yeah. Yeah, you have
to get dressed.

31:59.918 --> 32:02.321
I got clothes for you.

32:02.354 --> 32:04.890
I love you.

32:04.923 --> 32:07.159
I love you.

