39:52.123 --> 39:54.893
Go now.

39:54.926 --> 39:55.894
[ Door closes ]

39:55.927 --> 39:57.629
[ Grunts ]

39:57.663 --> 40:00.098
[ Groans ]

40:00.131 --> 40:02.768
No, look at me.

40:02.801 --> 40:04.903
Look at me.

40:09.107 --> 40:11.510
I was a good boy.

40:13.479 --> 40:14.713
[ Grunts ]

